Level 1 - 

 quest 1 - Escape your prison cell when Lillits come to check on you. (Reward: Lillit Pistols)
 quest 2 - Kill surrounding Lillit gaurds 
 quest 3 - Unlock lower cells with Lillit chief-guard key 
 quest 4 - Find Elevator Key 
 quest 5 - Fight another 25 Lillits upstairs 
 quest 6 - Unlock upper cells
 quest 7 - Get into Warden room 
 quest 8 - Fight Warden Boss 
 quest 9 - Escape outside 
 quest 10 - Fight creatures 
 quest 11 - Find ship 
